------------------test join
set _enable_storage_cardinality_estimation = 1;
show variables like "%storage_cardinality_estimation%";
Variable_name	Value
_enable_storage_cardinality_estimation	ON
explain select * from test a,test b where a.c2=11 and b.c2=11 and a.c1=b.c3;
Query Plan
===================================================
|ID|OPERATOR          |NAME |EST.ROWS|EST.TIME(us)|
---------------------------------------------------
|0 |MERGE JOIN        |     |18      |99          |
|1 |├─TABLE RANGE SCAN|a(p1)|17      |49          |
|2 |└─TABLE RANGE SCAN|b(p2)|17      |49          |
===================================================
